137
00:05:35,397 --> 00:05:39,088
Mr. Shen, who was dispatched
by the group's headquarters.

138
00:05:39,487 --> 00:05:40,367
Let's welcome him.

139
00:05:44,408 --> 00:05:44,968
Alright.

140
00:05:45,447 --> 00:05:46,447
Second,

141
00:05:47,048 --> 00:05:50,768
