for everyone.

142
00:05:51,367 --> 00:05:51,968
Please.

143
00:05:54,088 --> 00:05:56,007
I'll skip the formalities.

144
00:05:56,968 --> 00:05:58,168
My purpose here

145
00:05:59,048 --> 00:06:02,208
is to investigate the project delays.

146
00:06:05,848 --> 00:06:07,408
Of course there are issues.

147
00:06:08,327 --> 00:06:10,848
All the problems
are laid out plain as day.

148
00:06:11,528 --> 00:06:13,848
Investor Mr. Wu ran off with the money

149
00:06:14,088 --> 00:06:17,048
and wronged all my workers, right?

150
00:06:17,048 --> 00:06:17,487
Right.

151
00:06:17,487 --> 00:06:18,807
Funds were depleted after he ran.

152
00:06:18,807 --> 00:06:19,608
Right?

153
00:06:19,648 --> 00:06:20,088
Right.

154
00:06:20,168 --> 00:06:21,168
As for those funds...

155
00:06:21,807 --> 00:06:22,807
Quiet down! Quiet!

156
00:06:23,367 --> 00:06:24,768
Let Mr. Shen finish speaking.

157
00:06:26,887 --> 00:06:28,327
Regarding Wu Chengming's case,

158
00:06:28,528 --> 00:06:29,608
I'll handle it for sure.

159
00:06:30,288 --> 00:06:32,048
What I need to emphasize today is

160
00:06:32,927 --> 00:06:33,848
these days,

161
00:06:34,447 --> 00:06:35,528
I've discovered

162
00:06:35,608 --> 00:06:37,247
that at this site,

163
00:06:37,927 --> 00:06:40,088
major construction issues have surfaced.

164
00:06:40,807 --> 00:06:43,528
The steel reinforcement has been exposed
to the elements too long,

165
00:06:43,728 --> 00:06:44,648
causing oxidation.

166
00:06:45,927 --> 00:06:49,088
Delayed window installations

167
00:06:50,048 --> 00:06:52,032
left walls and ground waterlogged

168
00:06:52,448 --> 00:06:54,327
and all pipelines moldy.

169
00:06:55,088 --> 00:06:57,408
Missing wire mesh reinforcement

170
00:06:58,168 --> 00:06:59,327
has resulted in slab cracks.

171
00:07:00,567 --> 00:07:01,927
Due to these failures,

172
00:07:01,927 --> 00:07:03,288
immediate rectification and rework

173
00:07:03,327 --> 00:07:03,927
are required.

174
00:07:04,487 --> 00:07:06,048
Rework? With no pay?

175
00:07:06,927 --> 00:07:08,247
Show us the money first.

176
00:07:09,007 --> 00:07:10,007
Why is rework needed?

177
00:07:10,127 --> 00:07:11,887
Mr. Shen is demanding wildly.

178
00:07:12,327 --> 00:07:14,048
Even from your office,

179
00:07:14,288 --> 00:07:16,487
