inside and out.

180
00:07:18,048 --> 00:07:19,567
Did you hear him, department heads?

181
00:07:19,848 --> 00:07:20,848
Okay. Rework.

182
00:07:21,048 --> 00:07:22,367
You need money for that.

183
00:07:22,927 --> 00:07:23,608
Mr. Shen,

184
00:07:24,487 --> 00:07:26,168
the group has no allocated budget.

185
00:07:26,327 --> 00:07:28,247
What can we proceed

186
00:07:28,528 --> 00:07:29,408
and rework with?

187
00:07:29,447 --> 00:07:29,848
Right.

188
00:07:29,887 --> 00:07:30,327
Am I right?

189
00:07:30,367 --> 00:07:30,848
Exactly.

190
00:07:31,048 --> 00:07:31,848
There's no money.

191
00:07:32,168 --> 00:07:33,807
It's mainly about money.

192
00:07:33,968 --> 00:07:35,327
No money, no rework.

193
00:07:35,367 --> 00:07:35,807
Right.

194
00:07:35,848 --> 00:07:36,528
Right?

195
00:07:36,648 --> 00:07:37,768
Without money...

196
00:07:37,807 --> 00:07:39,127
Quiet! Quiet!

197
00:07:39,768 --> 00:07:40,807
Quiet! Quiet!

198
00:07:44,288 --> 00:07:45,367
Lost control, have we?

199
00:07:47,127 --> 00:07:47,768
Everyone,

200
00:07:47,968 --> 00:07:49,687
we've collaborated for years.

201
00:07:49,807 --> 00:07:51,088
Challenges exist,

202
00:07:51,247 --> 00:07:53,127
but Mr. Shen's new here.

203
00:07:53,367 --> 00:07:54,768
He needs time to understand.

204
00:07:54,848 --> 00:07:57,088
How about this? Do me a favor.

205
00:07:57,288 --> 00:07:57,807
Let's...

206
00:07:57,848 --> 00:08:02,048
We followed
the company's guidelines, right?

207
00:08:02,247 --> 00:08:04,757
Now you are accusing us
of non-compliance baselessly.

208
00:08:04,757 --> 00:08:05,728
That's not fair!

209
00:08:06,208 --> 00:08:07,048
That's not fair!

210
00:08:07,088 --> 00:08:07,528
Exactly!

211
00:08:07,567 --> 00:08:08,168
Right?

212
00:08:08,848 --> 00:08:11,288
Produce your individual contracts.

213
00:08:12,168 --> 00:08:14,288
We'll verify construction quality

214
00:08:14,487 --> 00:08:17,648
against initial specifications.

215
00:08:18,048 --> 00:08:20,968
No individual contracts.
We're just subcontractors.

216
00:08:21,807 --> 00:08:24,447
Then we'll sign
new individual contracts today.

217
00:08:25,447 --> 00:08:27,048
How to sign that?

218
00:08:27,408 --> 00:08:28,007
Exactly.

219
00:08:28,088 --> 00:08:31,447
The contracts specify
construction standards.

220
00:08:32,608 --> 00:08:37,367
(Labor Contract)
Compliant ones receive timely payments.

221
00:08:38,247 --> 00:08:40,648
Non-compliant work gets rectified

222
00:08:41,088 --> 00:08:43,968
with penalties for poor execution.

223
00:08:44,887 --> 00:08:46,648
All is clearly stipulated.

224
00:08:49,888 --> 00:08:50,727
Mr. Shen,

225
00:08:50,888 --> 00:08:52,447
