226
00:08:53,288 --> 00:08:56,368
I've managed projects for decades.

227
00:08:56,807 --> 00:08:58,768
These workers answer to me.

228
00:08:59,368 --> 00:09:01,847
We work under master contracts.
No individual contracts.

229
00:09:02,447 --> 00:09:04,168
You're breaking industry norms.

230
00:09:04,447 --> 00:09:05,847
It undermines my authority.

231
00:09:06,128 --> 00:09:07,248
No one will respect me.

232
00:09:07,368 --> 00:09:10,807
Our contracts
only govern construction standards

233
00:09:11,288 --> 00:09:12,447
and payment terms.

234
00:09:13,368 --> 00:09:15,048
No management authority is included.

235
00:09:15,727 --> 00:09:19,648
But from now on, all workers' salaries
won't go through your hands.

236
00:09:20,967 --> 00:09:26,048
And future financial audits
won't be a burden anymore.

237
00:09:26,727 --> 00:09:27,528
Isn't that good?

238
00:09:28,408 --> 00:09:29,168
Yes.

239
00:09:29,567 --> 00:09:30,648
It's great.

240
00:09:31,087 --> 00:09:32,408
It's great.

241
00:09:39,128 --> 00:09:41,128
