after work every day.

244
00:09:49,087 --> 00:09:50,768
Wages will be paid daily.

245
00:09:51,248 --> 00:09:52,087
Does your word count?

246
00:09:52,128 --> 00:09:53,528
Can we trust your word?

247
00:09:53,967 --> 00:09:54,768
Do you mean it?

248
00:09:54,847 --> 00:09:57,087
Those who agree can sign the contract.

249
00:09:57,528 --> 00:09:58,128
I'll sign it!

250
00:09:59,368 --> 00:10:00,168
No pushing.

251
00:10:00,727 --> 00:10:02,087
Stop shoving! Wait your turn.

252
00:10:02,087 --> 00:10:02,727
Mr. Shen,

253
00:10:03,128 --> 00:10:04,207
if you insist on this,

254
00:10:04,327 --> 00:10:05,768
