- Let's go!

258
00:10:09,288 --> 00:10:09,847
Let's go home.

259
00:10:10,008 --> 00:10:11,927
Li! Li, don't leave!

260
00:10:12,128 --> 00:10:13,087
Li, don't leave!

261
00:10:13,168 --> 00:10:13,727
