266
00:10:18,327 --> 00:10:19,087
Move aside.

267
00:10:19,248 --> 00:10:20,008
Don't go.

268
00:10:22,288 --> 00:10:23,207
Hello, Mr. Zhang?

269
00:10:24,087 --> 00:10:25,248
Come report

270
00:10:25,528 --> 00:10:26,967
