271
00:10:27,408 --> 00:10:28,087
Okay, Mr. Shen.

272
00:10:28,327 --> 00:10:29,927
I'll bring the whole tech team with me.

273
00:10:33,967 --> 00:10:34,648
Good.

274
00:10:35,408 --> 00:10:36,607
Don't regret this.

275
00:10:36,888 --> 00:10:37,488
Let's go!

276
00:10:37,967 --> 00:10:38,927
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

277
00:10:38,967 --> 00:10:39,687
Let's go.

278
00:10:39,687 --> 00:10:44,055
